{
  "stem": "5496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whether you are Muslim or Catholic or whatever it is, just be kind and good, for we all belong to the same race.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, it was most gratifying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The children all loved it, and the teacher gave me round of applause.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the teacher came over to me and thanked me so much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She said, that's the best lesson they could, indeed, have from somebody who has firsthand experience of hatred that is caused by hating each other and each other's religion.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I really can't think of anything in particular.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are many little incidents, but, you know, you can't think of them all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But primarily, as I said, I became a well-adjusted person.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still suffer of my chronic dislocation, but I live with it and I don't let it bother me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I do the best I can.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't do any physical labor, but, as I said, I managed, in my profession, to work all these many years, which was most satisfying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I love my family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Fred's sister-- we have a very small family-- Fred's sister Elaine, her son David, her daughter Ingrid, their son Michael, and we are very close.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I love my friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they all say I'm very giving, and I just love to see when people enjoy coming here and I can cause any joy in any form or shape to anyone.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To some extent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's-- the niece-- well, the-- oh, the niece does, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her son is too young, but her niece done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As the years went by, for some reason she always was told not to ask questions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, at the beginning, truly, we were always told, especially Aunt Rose.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I adjusted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But Aunt Rose talked about it always.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we would hear reprimands.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
